<div class="question">
<h2 class="question-title">你收到的最奇葩的礼物是什么？</h2>

<div class="answer">

<div class="meta">
<img class="avatar" src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4310da6e07b3e3a2ea36bd49c5c4e756_is.jpg">
<span class="author">sy DDDD</span>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>直接上图吧：</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/70/30c1d69fe107ee1fea4f41876f4ac875_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/70/f498011aec6a1ccd88ca55b9017792f0_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="answer">

<div class="meta">
<img class="avatar" src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg">
<span class="author">知乎用户</span>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>把我三年的体重数据，手动，一个一个的，输入到 Excel 里进行回归统计，做成了一个大盘走势图，然后忧心忡忡的提醒我要多吃点。</p>
<p>多！吃！点！</p>
<p>好不容易减下来的肥，他让我多吃点。</p>
<p>真 · 实验室待傻了 · 老实人。</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/70/v2-6005e4d106da1e983f1f1eb5cb2299d9_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="answer">

<div class="meta">
<img class="avatar" src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a94e016d6e63151f4ceb75564c5db324_is.jpg">
<span class="author">与人为善，</span><span class="bio">私信免去客套直奔主题，不免费回复文章中已详解过的问题，谢谢合作(｡ì _ í｡)</span>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>看到这里都是女生回答，我作为男生来扳回一局吧。</p>
<p>昨天我和朋友们过生日，我收到了一件让我有意外惊喜的生日礼物。</p>
<p>它</p>
<p>是</p>
<p>一</p>
<p>只</p>
<p>鸡</p>
<p>！</p>
<p>它长这样</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/70/v2-7ca5ccc3fe078b0b6130a444f2264d81_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>另一边长这样</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/70/v2-de658281a7b5a4e3c5bffc82ae2bd3f6_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>正面长这样</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/70/v2-74235bbc59bcd8d549c5a392642bd82d_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>高能预警，背面是密集恐惧症的福音</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/70/v2-aa8f7b1b0c24d11b796d48c5d18d47ba_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>我的花屁股好看吗？</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/70/v2-9d2d4fa88efa2d35f784a5d8d16f320b_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>我下巴上的鸡屎（胶水）性感吗？</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/70/v2-657ea7b95a4b6b489ff8745c87b7542f_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>我的眼睛很迷人</p>
<p><img class="content-image" src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/70/v2-4d5781e672515e14cf57e8bed48d097a_b.jpg" alt=""></p>
